#

Pumpkin Spice Waffles

25 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastBrunchFallComfort Food

Description

Deliciously fluffy waffles infused with warm pumpkin spice, perfect for a cozy breakfast.

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 1 ¾ cups
  • baking powder: 1 tablespoon
  • baking soda: 1 teaspoon
  • ground cinnamon: 1 teaspoon
  • ground nutmeg: ½ teaspoon
  • ground ginger: ½ teaspoon
  • salt: ½ teaspoon
  • pumpkin puree: 1 cup
  • milk: ¾ cup
  • eggs: 2
  • vanilla extract: 1 teaspoon
  • unsalted butter, melted: ½ cup
